Kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'abarwayi bose ba Coronavirus (COVID-19) wariyongereye cyane mu Burayi.
Umubare rusange w'abarwaye Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ibintu bisa mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, byerekana ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi gikomeje gukwirakwira mu bihugu byose nubwo kiri ku kigero gitandukanye bitewe n'ibihugu.
Ukurikije uburambe bw'Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bukabije bigomba kwitegura kurushaho mu gihe hagaragaye ubwiyongere bukabije bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, abantu bataramenyekana icyateye indwara ya Samba mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye iki cyorezo ari Coronavirus nshya, izwi nka Sars-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara iterwa n'ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 yiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu, ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko 80% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwaye indwara yoroheje, ni ukuvuga indwara y'ubuhumekero ifitanye isano n'ibicurane by'ibihaha cyangwa itari ifitanye isano na byo, kandi abenshi barakira.
Mu bantu 14% barwaye kanseri, COVID-19 iba ikomeye cyane bigatuma umuntu akenera kujya mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6% baba barwaye cyane bigatuma umuntu akenera kwitabwaho cyane.
4% by'abarwayi bari mu bitaro bavurwa COVID-19 ni bo bapfuye.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, tugereranya uko COVID-19 igenda muri buri gihugu cya EU/European Economic Area na Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika (UK) n'intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Twagereranyije imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/Afurika y'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza
COVID-19 yakomeje gukwirakwira mu bice byinshi by'isi, ikomeza kuva mu Bushinwa, kandi icyorezo cya COVID-19 ubu kirimo gukwirakwira ku isi yose.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo ku isi.
Spiteri et al. banditse ku rubuga rwa Eurosurveillance 2020 rwasohotse ku ya 5 Werurwe, batangaje ko ari bo bantu ba mbere b'i Burayi bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 hakurikijwe ibisobanuro by'abanduye na OMS.
Mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi, u Bufaransa ni bwo bwavuze abanduye batatu ba mbere ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020, baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu bose banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 30 byose bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, mu gihe kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2020 kugeza kuri uwo munsi hari abantu 39,768 banduye na 1,727 bapfuye, muri bo 17,750 banduye na 1,441 bapfuye mu Butaliyani honyine.
Kumenya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 n'ibyabaye muri rusange
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 muri buri gihugu ku isi nk'uko byatangajwe n'Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Gukumira Indwara (ECDC) ituruka gusa ku makuru y'ibiro by'ubuzima by'icyo gihugu, abayobozi b'ubuzima ku rwego rw'igihugu n'akarere na OMS, kandi ivugururwa buri munsi saa munani za mu gitondo.
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gupima imiterere ya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza no kuyigereranya n'u Butaliyani.
Kubera ko kuba hari abantu bafite COVID-19 ari ibintu bifatika, twasuzumye imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu gihe cy'iminsi 14, dufatiye ku mibare isanzwe ya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cya EU/European Economic Area no mu Bwongereza kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Byongeye kandi, twagereranyije imibare y'abanduye muri buri gihugu guhera saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020, n'iy'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza
Imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 y'icyorezo, yakurikiwe n'iyo mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) muri rusange (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Ku bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza muri rusange, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma wiyongera cyane ahagana ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Ibikoresho by'ubufasha).
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ukwiyongera kwihuse kw'ibyago byatangajwe biturutse mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza na byo byerekanye ko byiyongereye ku mubare w'ibyago bya COVID-19 (Ibikoresho by'ubufasha).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza imibare yose y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza ugereranyije n'umubare w'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Kugeza saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongereye cyane mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza.
Ibikorwa bya COVID-19 muri rusange byerekana ko icyorezo cy'isi yose kiri kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse mu bihugu byose.
Ibi birimo kuba mu bihugu bitandukanye, mu gihe hari itandukaniro mu bisubizo by'ubuzima rusange ku rwego rw'igihugu, ndetse wenda no mu bihugu bitandukanye, hari ibisobanuro bitandukanye by'uburwayi n'amabwiriza atandukanye yo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bamenye niba COVID-19 iriho.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu ntara z'Ubutaliyani zanduye iyi virus bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe muri izo ntara byararengeje ubushobozi, nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibitangazamakuru.
Kugeza ubu, amakuru ku barwayi ba COVID-19 bavurirwa mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu byumba by'indembe (data ntiyerekanwa) ni 6% na 1% gusa ku rwego rw'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi/akarere k'ubukungu bw'uburayi (EU/EEA).
Ariko kandi, bagomba gukusanya amakuru mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo bakomeze amakuru y'igihe cya vuba yo gukurikirana, yibanda ku mibare y'abavugwa n'abapfa.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari itandukaniro rinini hagati y'ibitanda by'indembe n'ibitanda bisanzwe, kuva ku bitanda 29.2 mu Budage kugeza ku bitanda 4.2 muri Porutugali ku bantu 100,000.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kuba bifite ubukungu bwinshi cyangwa buke ugereranyije n'Ubutaliyani (ibitanda 12.5 byo kwitaho cyane no kwita ku bantu 100,000, mu 201011).
Imimerere yo mu rwego rwo hejuru yo kurinda indwara zidakira, ifitanye isano n'ubushobozi bwo kwivuza, ihuriyeho n'ibyago birenga 90 byo kurara ku buriri bw'abarwayi bakomeye. Umubare w'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 byerekanwe mu bigo by'amacumbi muri buri gihugu cya EU / EEA n'Ubwongereza, byatanzwe mu byiciro bya gatandatu bya ECDC.
Kubera ko hari umubare munini w'abarwayi mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bikunze gukorera igice runaka cy'abaturage, amakuru yerekeye abarwayi n'ibitanda by'indembe bigomba gutangwa ku rwego rwa Statistique 2 (NUTS-2).
Ibyabaye mu Butaliyani n'ibindi bikorwa mu bindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi hose kirimo gukwirakwira mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku barwayi bakomeye, rero, bigomba kwitegura kuko SARS-CoV-2 ikomeje gukwirakwira mu baturage kandi umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho n'ubuzima, cyane cyane abarwayi bakomeye, urimo kwiyongera, nk'uko byagenze mu turere tw'Ubutaliyani twanduye virusi.
Nkuko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago bya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse kandi bwuzuye bwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-COV-2 ni ngombwa, aho gukomeza icyorezo ku buryo bwo kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera vuba kwitezwe mu mubare w'abanduye bitabaye mu gihe cyagenwe, ntabwo biha umwanya uhagije abashyiraho ibyemezo n'ibitaro kugirango basobanukirwe, bemere kandi bahindure ibisubizo byabo.
Gusuzuma ibyago byihuse bigabanya ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zigamije kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo ku isi.
Amasaha ibihugu bishobora kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima, ni macye.
Bitabaye ibyo, inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu byo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi zishobora kuzamurwa mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere n'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) cyatewe n'indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (Sars) Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), imaze guhitana abantu barenga 80.000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, ihitana abarenga 3,000.
Nk'uko virusi ya SARS-CoV yandura abantu ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwandura binyuze mu birura kandi igatuma abantu bagaragaza ibimenyetso nk'ibyo.
Icyakora, nubwo COVID-19 ifite igipimo cyo gupfa gito ugereranyije na SARS, igipimo cy'uburangare ni kinini kandi cyandura abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abagore kurusha abakiri bato.
Kubera ko hari inyandiko nyinshi zisohoka ku ndwara nshya, iyi nyandiko igerageza gutanga isesengura rihoraho kandi ryuzuye ry'umushinga w'ubushakashatsi ugenda wiyongera.
Tuzabagezaho ibibazo by'ibanze bijyanye n'indwara, indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu, virusi, uburyo bwo kugenzura, kuvura no kwirinda.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko ubu bushakashatsi buzafasha abantu gusobanukirwa no kwirinda iyi ndwara iteje akaga.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza Umunsi Mukuru w'Igisibo wabaye ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020, byasigaye ari ibintu bitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose, kubera ko Abashinwa baburiwe kuguma mu ngo zabo mu gihe cy'uwo munsi mukuru no nyuma yawo, kubera icyorezo gishya cy'agakoko gatera indwara.
Iyi virusi isa cyane na coronavirus (Cov) yateje indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero mu 2003, ku mpamvu y'ibyo, ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryayise SARS-CoV-2, naho indwara ifitanye isano na yo yitwa COVID-19.
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, gikwirakwira mu gihugu cyose mu buryo bwihuse, kigera mu bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kugeza ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, imibare y'abanduye COVID-19 yari imaze kurenga 80,000, abarenga 40,000 barekuwe, naho abarenga 3,000 barapfuye.
OMS iraburira ko COVID-19 ari umwanzi wa mbere ku isi kandi ko ishobora kwangiza kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri kuva raporo ya mbere yasohotse ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, inyandiko zirenga 200 ku COVID-19 zanditswe, harimo Virology, Epidemiology, Etiology, Diagnostics and Treatment, zigaragaza uko virusi zatandukanyijwe n'abarwayi batandukanye.
Ubu bushakashatsi bugerageza gusobanura mu buryo buhinnye ibyo bagezeho mu bushakashatsi bushya kandi buhindagurika vuba.
Uko bishoboka kose, tugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na COVID, indwara y'ubuhumekero yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, icyorezo cyo mu 2012).
Tuzasuzuma ibyo tumaze kumenya ku birebana no kwirinda no kumenya amateka y'iyo ndwara, ndetse n'ibindi bibazo byihutirwa.
CoVs zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zisanzwe zidakora ku bantu, kandi ni zo zitera cyane ibicurane bya 4 bigera kuri 15%.
Ariko kandi, muri iki kinyejana twahuye inshuro ebyiri na CoVs nini cyane zitera indwara (SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV); ubwa mbere mu Bushinwa mu 2003 na Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, hanyuma zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi, zigatanga indwara n'urupfu biteye ubwoba.
Ku bw'ibyo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyo muri iki gihe ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya CoV mu mateka y'abantu.
Nkuko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1, abantu bataramenyekana bafite indwara ya Samba batangiye gutangarizwa Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, umurwayi wa COVID-19 yarekuwe.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, urupfu rwa mbere rwanditswe mu mazi.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, mu bihugu no mu bihugu bituranye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abashinzwe ubuzima batangaje ko iyi virusi yanduye, byerekana ko ishobora kwandura umuntu ku wundi.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, imodoka zose zitwara abagenzi mu mujyi wa Wuhan zahagaze, kandi ibikorwa byose by'umujyi birafungwa.
Ubushakashatsi bw'ibanze bwakozwe ku ya 24 Mutarama bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 bagaragaweho ubwandu, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho byatekerejwe ko icyorezo cyaturutse mu matungo atazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingutu ku buzima ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yatunganywaga, iki cyorezo cyari cyamaze kugera mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo 2).2).
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka mu buryo bwihuse, urugero rwa nyuma rw'icyorezo n'uburemere bwacyo bishobora kuba bitaramenyekana.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo byinshi ku barwayi 8,866, muri bo 4,021 bari bafite COVID-19 kandi bagaragazaga ubwandu bushya (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira abantu b'imyaka yose ariko cyane cyane abafite imyaka iri hagati ya 30 na 65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abanduye virusi bafite imyaka irenga 50, bake cyane bari munsi ya 20, kandi 14 gusa ni bo bafite munsi y'imyaka 10.
