Mu bindi bikorwa byo kuvura cytocin storm harimo gutera ingufu mu mubiri mu kurwanya indwara z'ingirabuzimafatizo za T; kubuza IFN-γ, IL-1, na TNF; kubuza JAK; Blinatumumab; cytokine signaling inhibitor 4; na HDAC inhibitors.
Steroids zikoreshwa cyane mu kuvura SARS mu rwego rwo kugabanya ibyago byo kwangirika kw'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kurwanya indwara.
Ariko, ibipimo byinshi bya siteroyide nta cyo bifasha mu kugabanya kwangirika kw'ibihaha bikomeye mu barwayi ba SARS na COVID-19.
Ahubwo, bishobora kugira ingaruka zikomeye ku kuntu indwara igenda ikura, bigatuma umuntu apfa, cyane cyane mu magufwa.
Ariko, ingano yoroheje cyangwa iri hagati ya corticosteroids z'igihe gito zisabwa ku barwayi bakomeye ba COVID-19.
Mu gihe iyi nkuru yandikwaga, nta muti wa virusi wari waragaragaye ko ufasha abantu.
Icyakora, umuti witwa remdesivir, uvanaho ingano ya nucleotide, watangiwe mu murwayi umwe wo muri Amerika ufite COVID-19, wagaragaje ko ufite akamaro.
Remdesivir ni umuti mushya wa virusi wakozwe na Gilead, watangijwe ugenewe kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma yaho, Remdesivir yagaragaye ko ihagarika ibikorwa bya virusi imwe ya RNA, harimo virusi ya MERS na SARS.
Mu buryo buhuje n'ibyo, Gilead yashyikirije Ubushinwa ibikoresho byayo kugira ngo bikore igerageza ry'ibipimo ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi ibisubizo byitezwe cyane.
Byongeye kandi, barisitinib, interferon-α, lopinavir/ritonavir na ribavirin byatanzwe mu buryo bwo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara ikomeye yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero.
Isesemi, kugira iseseme, gusubiranamo, kwangirika kw'umwijima n'ibindi bibazo bishobora guterwa no gukoresha imiti ivanze na Lopinavir/Ritonavir.
Iyo imiti ikoreshwa hamwe n'indi ikoreshwa mu barwayi, igomba kugenzurwa neza.
Gukora plasma n'udupira tw'abanduye tuvuye mu barwayi bakize
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, abantu bamaze igihe kirekire bavurwa indwara zandura, kandi bakoresha amaraso y'abantu bakize kugira ngo bavurwe cyangwa barinde abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza.
Birumvikana ko abarwayi bakize indwara bafite ibipimo by'abanduye indwara biri hejuru y'iby'iyo ndwara mu maraso yabo.
Imirambo ni immunoglobuline (Ig) ikorwa na B lymphocyte, irwanya udukoko dutera indwara n'ibindi bintu by'amahanga, kandi ikanagabanya imikorere y'uduporeke dutandukanye mu turemangingo dutera indwara.
Muri iyo gahunda, plasma y'amaraso yakuwe mu barwayi bakize COVID-19 yahawe abarwayi 10 barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byaragabanutse mu masaha 24, bigabanya ububabare bw'ibisebe n'ubukana bwa virusi, ndetse n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu maraso.
Ariko kandi, kugeza igihe habonekeye uburyo bwo kuvura, hagomba kubaho ibimenyetso n'ibitekerezo kugira ngo hagaragazwe uburyo bwo gukoresha cyane.
Nanone kandi, hari ibintu bimwe na bimwe bishobora guteza akaga bitewe na plazima bigomba kwitabwaho cyane, bitewe n'ingaruka z'iyo miti.
Urugero, abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora gutuma umubiri utagira icyo ukora ku mubiri, bigatuma habaho indwara y'ubushyuhe butera indwara yitwa syndrome de la déshydratation cytokinique.
Akenshi, ingano y'abanduye amaraso iba iri hasi, kandi plasma ikenerwa cyane mu kuvura abarwayi barembye.
Guhanga no gukora vuba udukoko tw'ubwirinzi runaka dushobora kurwanya icyorezo cy'icyorezo biragoye.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni ngombwa gutandukanya insoro za B n'abarwayi bakize no kumenya kode za jenome z'ingenzi mu gukora za poroteyine z'agakoko zigira ingaruka nziza cyangwa se kuzisuzuma kugira ngo zigire ingaruka nziza.
Ibyo bituma dushobora kongera ingano y'abanduye mu buryo bworoshye.
TCM yakoreshejwe mu Bushinwa mu myaka ibihumbi byinshi mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Ariko kandi, ingaruka z'ibyo bikoresho ahanini ziba zishingiye ku buryo bwo kubikoresha, kandi uburyo bwo kubikora butandukanye bitewe n'uburwayi.
Ibyinshi mu bice by'ingenzi by'umubiri byakomeje kuba ibintu bitazwi cyangwa bidafite ibisobanuro, kubera ko kumenya no kwemeza ibyo bice cyangwa ibyo bice by'umubiri byari bigoye.
Muri iki gihe, TCM yabaye imwe mu miti y'ingenzi yo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje cyangwa bakize indwara bitewe no kubura uburyo bwiza kandi bwihariye bwo kuvura COVID-19.
Urugero, ibinini bya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen byabonetse ko bifite akamaro mu kuvura COVID-19.
Mu ntara nyinshi zo mu Bushinwa zakoresheje TCM ku barwayi 87% mu gihe umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 warutaga uwo mu zindi, harimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%).
Ariko kandi, ibyo bigereranyo ntibihagije, kubera ko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigomba kwitabwaho mu gihe cyo kubisuzuma, urugero nk'umubare w'abarwayi n'urugero rw'indwara.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boli Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bagereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'iburengerazuba (WM) n'uburyo bwo kuvura bw'ibanze (WM) hamwe na TCM.
Basanze igihe cyo kugarura ubushyuhe, igihe cyo kugabanya ibimenyetso no kumara igihe mu bitaro byagabanutse cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'iryo mu itsinda rya WM gusa.
Igitangaje kurushaho, ni uko umubare w'indwara z'uburwayi (kuva ku boroheje kugeza ku ndwara zikomeye) wagabanutse cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%); kandi umubare w'abapfa wagabanutse cyane mu itsinda rya WM+TCM ugereranyije n'itsinda rya WM gusa (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Ariko, ubuziranenge n'umutekano wa TCM bizategereza ibisubizo by'ibigeragezo bikomeye kandi bigenzurwa cyane mu bigo byinshi.
Gusobanura uburyo bwo gufata ingamba no gusobanura ibice by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi bwa TCM cyangwa niba bishoboka, guhuza nabyo birashobora gushishikaza cyane.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko bafite COVID-19 bafite ubwoba bw'indwara yandura cyane kandi ishobora kwica, kandi abantu bari mu kato bumva bataye umutwe, bafite irungu n'uburakari.
Nanone kandi, ingaruka mbi z'indwara n'imiti, urugero nk'umuriro, guhumeka nabi no gukorora, urugero nk'ibitotsi biterwa na corticosteroids, bishobora gutuma umuntu arushaho kurwara indwara zo mu mutwe no kwiheba.
Mu byiciro bya mbere by'icyorezo cya SARS, hari ibimenyetso bitandukanye by'indwara zo mu mutwe, harimo guhora mu bwiherero, guhangayika, guhungabana, guhungabana, ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe, guhungabana no gutekereza kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abantu ku gahato, kimwe mu bisubizo by'ubuzima bw'abaturage mu kwirinda icyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu bahangayikishwa n'icyorezo, ingaruka z'igikorwa cyo kwigunga no kwigunga n'imiryango yabo n'inshuti.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu barwaye COVID-19, abakekwaho ubwandu n'abahuye na bo, kandi muri rusange bakeneye kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe, bagomba kwitabwaho.
Ubufasha bw'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe, gutanga amakuru y'igihe cyagenwe kandi y'ukuri ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 n'imigambi y'ubuvuzi, no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'imikorere ya porogaramu kugira ngo umuntu yirinde guhura n'abandi.
Uretse kuba inkingo z'indwara z'ibicurane z'ibitunguru n'iz'abantu bafite virusi z'ibicurane ari ingenzi mu guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara z'ibicurane, ni n'umufasha mu kurwanya indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bushya.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya SARS-CoV, hakozwe ingamba zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S zishobora kongera abasirikare b'umubiri n'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara.
Inkingo ziterwa na virusi zitera indwara zigeragejwe mu nyamaswa kuri SARS.
Ariko kandi, niba izo nkingo z'abakandida zifite ingaruka ku bageze mu za bukuru, uburyo bwo kugabanya ubwandu n'uburyo bwo kurwanya virusi zandura mu matungo, bigomba kwemezwa mbere y'uko igeragezwa ry'ubuvuzi ritangira.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa n'uko SARS yagabanutse mu myaka 17 ishize kandi nta muntu mushya wigeze avurwa kuva icyo gihe.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, ubwandu bwa Maresi Kenza mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati bwakomeje kwiyongera cyane, aho bwanduriraga ku bantu buvuye ku matungo, maze bukagera no mu tundi turere.
Uburyo bwo gukingira indwara ya MERS bwakozwe hifashishijwe virusi zidakora, plazmide za ADN, poroteyine z'ubwoko butandukanye, ibintu bimeze nk'udupira tw'inshuro nto, utunyangingo duto cyane, utunyangingo tumeze nk'udukoko na poroteyine zo muri laboratwari, kandi zimwe muri zo zagejejwe ku nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwizewe kandi rukora neza rwo kwirinda SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu bafite uburwayi budafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda, ni igikorwa cyihutirwa kandi cy'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo gikomeje.
Ariko, guhangana n'ikibazo ni ikibazo bitewe n'igihe kirekire cyo gukora urukingo (amezi 18 ku kigereranyo) hamwe n'imiterere ya CoVs.
Kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, uburyo bwuzuye bwo kwivuza ku barwayi ibihumbi n'ibihumbi ni bwo bwonyine bwarangiye.
Akenshi abarwayi barakira buhoro buhoro kandi nta ngaruka mbi bigira ku buzima bwabo.
Ariko, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 ituma abantu barwara cyane kandi bagapfa.
Ni ngombwa rero kubaka uburyo bwo guhanura uko iyi ndwara izagenda kugira ngo inzego z'ubuzima zishobore gushyira mu bikorwa serivisi zazo, cyane cyane mu turere tudafite amikoro.
