Imyaka: Imyaka ni ingenzi mu kumenya amateka ya SARS, kandi ni nako bimeze kuri COVID-19.
Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866, bwagaragaje ko 47.7% by'abarwayi barengeje imyaka 50 bafite COVID-19 ahanini bari mu kigero cy'imyaka 30-65.
