Igitsina: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, SARS-CoV-2 yibasira abagabo cyane kurusha abagore (0.31/100.000 abagabo, 0.27/100.000 abagore).
Ibibazo by'ubuzima n'indwara zikunda kubaho: Abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara umutima n'ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ibibazo by'umutima ni byo bituma abarwayi ba SARS bapfa cyane.
SARS-CoV-2 bivugwa ko ifitanye isano na choline collagenase z'indwara ya ACE2-positive, ishobora gutera ibibazo by'ubuziranenge mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni ngombwa kumenya ko imyaka n'uburwayi biri mu bintu bifitanye isano kandi ko bishobora guhungabanya ubuzima bw'umuntu.
Ibimenyetso bya laboratwari bidakwiriye: Ibipimo bya poroteyine igira ibisubizo bya C (CRP) mu maraso bigaragaza urugero rw'ubuhumekero cyangwa kwangirika kw'imyakura, kandi byatanzwe ko bikoreshwa mu kumenya amateka y'uburwayi, gusubiza imiti no mu gihe cyo gukira.
Ubufatanye hagati y'ibipimo bya CRP n'ibimenyetso bya COVID-19 by'uburemere n'iterambere na byo byatangajwe.
Byongeye kandi, kongera laktate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT), na creatine kinase (CK) bishobora gufasha mu kwemeza ingaruka.
Izo enzymes z'ubumara zisohoka mu bice bitandukanye by'umubiri, cyane cyane mu mutima no mu gifu, iyo hari ingingo z'umubiri zangijwe.
Bityo rero, ibibazo by'umutima cyangwa iby'umwijima ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'ubuvuzi: Radiografi y'agafu n'igihe ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi bimara, hamwe n'ibindi bintu bigomba kurebwa kugira ngo hategerezwe ingaruka za COVID-19 n'ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, Steroids zikoreshwa cyane mu buvuzi bwunganira indwara zandura mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'umubiri n'ubukana bw'ubuhumekero.
Kubera ko abantu benshi barwaye SARS bakoreshaga corticosteroids nyinshi, abenshi mu barokotse indwara y'ibicurane by'amagufa, ubumuga budashira n'ubuzima bubi.
Ku bw'ibyo, niba ari ngombwa, siteroyi zigomba gukoreshwa mu rugero ruciriritse kandi mu gihe gito ku barwayi ba COVID-19.
