Ariko kandi, menya ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, kandi ko ubushakashatsi n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi biriyongera buhoro buhoro, bitewe n'ibyagezweho mu bushakashatsi n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi, bityo uburyo bwo kuyisuzuma no kuyivura bugakomeza kunonosorwa.
