Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'ingendo cyangwa gutura mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa uturere tuwukikije, aho abantu banduye COVID-19 bagaragaye mu minsi 14 mbere y'izamuka ry'ibimenyetso, cyangwa abandi bantu banduye COVID-19, (2) amateka yo guhura n'abantu banduye SARS-CoV-2 (bifashishije ibizamini bya alumic acid), (3) amateka yo guhura n'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije mbere y'izamuka ry'ibimenyetso, cyangwa abandi bantu banduye COVID-19 mu baturage, (4) urutonde rw'abantu banduye mu byumweru 2 mu duce duto (ni ukuvuga mu ngo, mu biro, mu ngo, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka; (2) ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) Umubare w'utugingo duto tw'amaraso yera, tugaragaraho umubare usanzwe, ugabanutse, cyangwa ugabanutse w'utugingo tw'amaraso mu cyiciro cya mbere.
