Hari byinshi bizagaragara kuri COVID-19 mu gihe kiri imbere, kandi Australia izita ku kugenzura imipaka no guhanahana amakuru mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Australia, habaye ibyihutirwa byo kwirinda indwara ziterwa n'ibinyabuzima.
Mu rwego rwo gushyiraho uburyo bwiza bwo gupima imodoka zitwara abagenzi mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi biteganya gucyura abaturage babyo n'abakozi ba dipolomasi mu gihugu cyabo, cyane cyane mu ndege z'icyo gihugu, binyuze mu guha uburenganzira abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Australia, Ubufaransa, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni byo bihugu bya mbere bitegura ingendo z'abaturage babyo gusa.
Pakistan ntizongera kwirukana umuturage wayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Burezili yirukanye Abanyabrezili 34 cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, Umushina umwe n'Abahinde.
Indege y'igihugu cya Brazil yaturutse muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde mbere yo kujya muri Brezil.
Abaturage bo muri Brezili bari bagiye i Huán, bari baratorotse ikigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi y'ahitwa Jubrás-Lea.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanaada 215 (176 bari muri iyo ndege, na 39 bari mu yindi yari yaraguzwe na Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika) bavuye mu mazi binjira muri CFB Trenton, aho bari bamaze ibyumweru bibiri mu kato.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 yageze muri CFB Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Ositaraliya bafashe abaturage 277 babajyana mu kigo cyo gufungira ku kirwa cya Noheli, aho bamaze iminsi 14 mu kato.
Indege y'i New Zealand yageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare, abagenzi bayo (harimo bamwe muri Australia na Pacific) bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare cya gisirikare cya Wuhan i Gapparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gucyura abaturage bazo bari ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Indege y'Abanyakanada 129 yari itwaye abagenzi yavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, igwa i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'u Buhinde yatangiye gucyura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege y'indege ya South African Airlines yasubije muri Afurika y'Epfo abaturage 112.
Abaturage bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragayeho ibimenyetso bya coronavirus, barasuzumwe mbere yo gutaha, bagasubirwamo mu rwego rwo kwirinda kwandura.
Abanyafurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragaje ko nta bimenyetso bya virusi bafite, ni bo basubijwe mu bihugu byabo.
Ibizamini byagaragariye ko abanyafurika y'epfo bose, harimo abakozi bose b'indege, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bari mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort, bafite ubuzima bwiza.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukuraho igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo cyugarije isi.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byohereje imfashanyo mu Bushinwa.
Hari amakuru avuga ko abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa biga muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika, bafatanyije n'itsinda ry'abakozi bo mu Bushinwa, batanze udupfukamunwa n'udupfukamunwa 50,000 bya N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama, kugira ngo bafashe mu bice byibasiwe n'iyo virusi. Umuryango wita ku bufasha bw'abantu witwa Direct Relief, ufatanyije na FedEx, wongeyeho udupfukamunwa n'udupfukamunwa 200,000, kandi wohereje ibikoresho bitandukanye byo kwirinda icyorezo nk'ama gants n'ama gamu ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union by'indege z'ubutabazi.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bagiye gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya WHO mu gufasha mu bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi ku rukingo no kuvura muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na Interaction, Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa 3.16 muri Wuhan, mu mujyi wa Walla, ku ya 6 Gashyantare, Ubushinwa bwohereje udupfukamunwa 200.000 muri Filipine.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko igiye kohereza imfashanyo ya miliyoni $2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze miliyoni imwe y'udupfukamunwa n'udupfukamunwa ku gihugu cya Wuhan, Turukiya yatanze toni 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwatanze toni 18 z'amaboko ku gihugu cya Wuhan, u Budage bwatanze toni 10,000 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Amerika yatanze toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi ku gihugu cy'Ubushinwa, kandi yiyemeza gutanga miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ku gihugu cyibasiwe na virusi.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'u Burusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'inzobere mu gufasha u Butaliyani bwari bwaratewe na coronavirus.
Umucuruzi Jack Ma yohereje ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1 by'imashini, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'imyenda 60,000 yo kurinda ku mugabane wa Afurika, i Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia.
Nyuma yaho, yohereje muri Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na za 'air conditioner' 5.
U Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje impungenge ku bipfunyika n'ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yambuye igihugu ibikoresho 58,000 byo gupima coronavirus byakozwe n'Ubushinwa kubera ko byari bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30%. Mu buryo nk'ubwo, u Buholandi bwashyizeho ibipfukamunwa 600.000 byakozwe n'Ubushinwa bidakomeye.
Ububiligi bwasubije udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa, twatangiriye mu Bushinwa ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije inkunga yihutirwa ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye abayobozi b'Ubushinwa ku bw'ibikorwa byo kurwanya iki cyorezo.
"WHO yagereranyije icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2004 na 2004, abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bakomeje kucyitondera, bituma imihati yo kwirinda no kucyirinda ihagarara, kandi iki kibazo kiri mu maboko ya leta nkuru ""gutanga amakuru ya buri gihe yo kwirinda ubwoba mbere y'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi"."
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, Imana Gale, uhagarariye Umuryango w'Abibumbye, yavuze ko icyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'ibanze cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo muri Wuhan ari icyemezo cy'ingenzi kandi kitigeze kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange, nubwo atari inama y'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima. Ku ya 30 Mutarama, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara y'ibyorezo (PHEIC) cyateye impungenge mpuzamahanga nyuma yo kwemezwa ko cyanduye umuntu ku wundi hanze y'Ubushinwa kandi umubare w'abantu mu bindi bihugu wiyongereye, icyo gikorwa kikaba ari icya gatandatu PHEIC itangaje kuva icyorezo cya mbere cy'ibicurane bya Swine Flu cyatangira mu 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC "ibanze ku bihugu bifite amikoro make n'abifite ubukungu buciriritse, bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza".
Ku bijyanye n'ibisubizo ku itegeko ryo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo guhungabanya ingendo mpuzamahanga n'ubucuruzi" kandi ko "Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ritagusaba guhagarika ingendo n'ubucuruzi".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye inkunga y'amadolari miliyoni 675 y'Amerika mu bihugu bifite amikoro make kugira ngo byongere kwitegura.
Bwana Tedros yavuze ko "Turi abanyantege nke cyane, ariko dukomeye cyane", asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwishyura byinshi nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, mu itangazo ry'itangazamakuru, OMS yise icyorezo COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye ko imbaraga zose za Loni zizasubiza.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buyobozi bw'Ibiza, ryatangijwe n'itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'ibiza, rishobora guhuza ibisubizo by'umuryango w'abibumbye, bityo izindi nzego zikagira ubumenyi ku ngaruka z'icyorezo ku mibereho rusange y'abaturage, ubukungu n'iterambere.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda rya misiyo rifatanyije n'Ubushinwa riyobowe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangiye ibikorwa mu Bushinwa byo gufasha inzobere zo mu gihugu no ku isi gusuzuma imiyoborere y'igihugu no kwakira amahugurwa n'inama. Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, WHO yavuze ko isi igomba gukora byinshi bishoboka mu kwitegura kugira ngo isuzume ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara n'intara, harimo ibigo by'ingenzi by'igihugu n'ibidukikije by'imijyi n'ibyaro.
"Mu gusubiza icyorezo muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'intumwa z'umushinga wo gusuzuma ikibazo. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko isesengura ry'ibyago bya coronavirus ku isi yose rizamuka rivuye kuri ""cyinshi"" rijya kuri ""cyinshi cyane"".
Umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda z'ibihe bidasanzwe z'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, Mike Ryan, yavuze ko "iki ari ikigeragezo nyacyo ku butegetsi bwose ku isi".
Iyi virusi ishobora kuza kandi ugomba kuba witeguye,  gufata ingamba zo kwirinda bizatuma isi yacu ishobora guhangana n'ibibi cyane.
"Ryan yongeyeho ko amakuru ariho ubu adatanga icyizere cy'uko abayobozi b'ubuzima rusange bavuga ko ari icyorezo ku isi hose, kuko bavuga ko "" twemeye ko abantu bose ku isi bashobora kwandura iyi virusi. " "
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo ku isi hose.
Umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima yavuze ko "yihebye cyane kubera umubare w'abantu bagaragaza ko bakwirakwira kandi ko bafite ikibazo cyo kutagira icyo bakora". Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryaramaganwe bikomeye kubera ko ritagenzuraga neza icyorezo, harimo no gutinda gutangaza ko ubuzima bw'abaturage bwihutirwa no gutinda kwemeza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi".
Imyigaragambyo yatumye Tewodros Adhanom, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima, yegura, ku itariki ya 6 Mata, abantu 733.000.
26 Werurwe 2020 Impuguke nyinshi mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu muri ONU zashyize imbaraga mu kwirinda ko uburenganzira bw'umuntu uwo ari we wese buhungabanywa muri iki cyorezo cya COVID-19.
Abahanga bavuga ko buri muntu wese afite inshingano yo gufatanya kurokora ubuzima, kandi leta nayo ifite inshingano yo kubikora.
Ishyirahamwe rivuga ko kubura umutungo cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba gukoreshwa mu gutera itsinda ry'abantu.
Abahanga bemeza ko buri muntu afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abamugaye, abanyamahanga, abageze mu za bukuru, abimukira, abatagira aho baba, abari mu bukene bukabije, abafunzwe, ndetse n'impunzi n'andi matsinda adasobanutse akeneye inkunga ya leta.
Imiryango mpuzamahanga y'ubutegetsi irimo kwifatanya mu gukemura ibibazo by'ubukungu n'imibereho byatewe na COVID-19.
Umuryango w'Ubutwererane n'Iterambere mu by'Ubukungu watangije urubuga rutanga ibisubizo by'igihe cyagenwe kandi byuzuye, ibitekerezo n'inama ku bihugu byo ku isi.
Gukomeza gahunda z'ubuzima n'ubukungu bw'isi binyuze mu ngamba zo guhangana n'ingaruka zo gufunga no guhagarika ingendo, gukemura ibibazo by'ibikoresho bya digitale birimo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu no gusubiza ibikorwa bya coronavirus, no kunoza igisubizo cy'isi yose.
Michelle Gove wo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, uvuye mu Bwongereza, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Bresil, Eduardo Borsono, banenze leta y'Ubushinwa bavuga ko iyi virusi yaturutse mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa, aho iyi ndwara yaturutse.
Bamwe mu bayobozi bo mu rwego rw'intara (CPC) mu Bushinwa bwo hagati birukanywe kubera kugenzura ibikorwa byo gushyira mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, mu kimenyetso cy'uko igisubizo cya politiki ku cyorezo muri utwo turere cyateje ibibazo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batekereza ko iki gikorwa cyafashwe mu rwego rwo kwirinda uburakari bw'abaturage kuri Xi Jinping, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishyaka ry'Abakomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa, ku cyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'Ubushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, banze ko icyorezo cya mbere cya coronavirus cyaturutse mu mazi, bashyigikira igitekerezo cy'uko COVID-19 ishobora kuba yaraturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
"Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump bwa Amerika bwise coronavirus ""virusi y'Ubushinwa"" cyangwa ""virusi ya Wuhan"" kubera ko Ubushinwa ""bwashyize imbaraga mu guhindura virusi idahwitse icyorezo ku isi"", mu gusubiza bamwe mu banenga bavuga ko ari urwikekwe rushingiye ku moko no ""kubera ko ubuyobozi bwe bwananiwe kugenzura iki cyorezo"".
The Daily Beast ivuga ko mu gihe cy'ubutegetsi bwa Amerika, nta kintu na kimwe kitagira ubuzima cyashoboraga kuvugwa nk'umuyoboro w'itumanaho, uretse Ubushinwa.
Abategetsi bo hanze, barimo Politiko, Politiki y'Igihugu n'Ikinyamakuru Bloomberg, bavuze ko imbaraga Ubushinwa bushyira mu kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe n'iyi virusi ari kimwe mu bigize ibikorwa byo kwamamaza ku rwego mpuzamahanga.
Joseph Borelli, umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi, yaburiye ko hari ikibazo cy'ingufu za politiki z'isi mu buryo bw'imikorere n'ibikorwa by'ubugiraneza.
Borrell yagize ati "Ubushinwa burimo gukwirakwiza ubutumwa bukomeye ko ari umufasha ushoboye kandi wizewe, bitandukanye na Amerika".
Ubushinwa bwongeye gufasha Venezuela na Iran, busaba Amerika kugabanya ibihano kuri Syria, Venezuela na Iran.
Udupfukamunwa 100,000 Jack Ma yatanze muri Cuba twabuzanyijwe n'ibihano bya Amerika ku ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Amerika bashinjwa gukoresha amafaranga y'ubufasha yari agenewe ibihugu by'amahanga mu gihugu cyabo.
Mu bihugu by'u Budage, Autriche, Suisse, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani, havugwa amakimbirane ku bijyanye no kwambara agapfukamunwa.
Turukiya kandi yafashe ibikoresho bifashishwa mu guhumeka bibarirwa mu magana byari byerekejwe muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi wanenze leta y'Ubutaliyani kubera ko itafatanyije n'Ubutaliyani, igihugu cyugarijwe na coronavirus.
"Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi, yagize ati ""Ubushinwa ni bwo bwonyine bwitabiriye mu buryo bubiri""".
Mu by'ukuri, ibi si urugero rwiza ku Burayi.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yavuganye kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Butaliyani Giuseppe Conte, maze afasha abaganga, ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye n'imodoka zitwara imiti kugera mu Butaliyani.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa, cyerekeje ku munyapolitiki ukomeye utifuje ko izina rye rigaragazwa, kivuga ko 80 ku ijana by'imfashanyo z'u Butaliyani nta cyo zimaze cyangwa nta cyo zivuze.
"Umusoko wanenze Uburusiya ko "buteza amakimbirane muri politiki n'ububanyi n'amahanga".
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, bashimiye itangazamakuru kuba ryarasobanuye neza amakuru.
Uburusiya bwohereje indege y'ubwikorezi bw'imiti muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov, yavuze ko "mu gihe [Putin] ashyigikiye abafatanyabikorwa ba Amerika, abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho by'Amerika bibonera imbaraga, kandi ko bashobora kongera kubikora bibaye ngombwa".
Imyitozo ya gisirikare ya NATO Defender 2020 , imyitozo ikomeye ya NATO kuva intambara y'ubutita irangiye, iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, izaba ku kigero cyo hasi.
Kate Hudson, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka riharanira guhashya intwaro za kirimbuzi, yanenze imyitozo ya Defender 2020. "Mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho, ntabwo ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi byugarijwe gusa, ahubwo n'ubw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bakoreramo bugeramiwe".
Ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, Perezida wa Irani, Hassan Rouhani, yanditse ibaruwa y'ibanze yoherereje leta z'ibihugu by'amahanga avuga ko ibihano by'ubukungu Amerika yafatiye iki gihugu ari imbogamizi ikomeye mu kurwanya iki cyorezo. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika ishyiraho politiki yihuta y'imibereho myiza ijyanye n'ibindi bihugu byateye imbere (ubuvuzi mpuzamahanga, kurinda abana ku isi hose, ingengo y'imari ihenze y'ibikorwaremezo by'ubuzima, n'ibindi).
Abashakashatsi mu bya politiki bavuze ko ibyo bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bwa Donald Trump bwo kongera gutorwa mu matora ya Perezida yo mu 2020. Imishyikirano ya dipolomasi na Japon na Koreya y'Epfo yaragabanutse kubera icyorezo.
Koreya y'Epfo "yashinje u Buyapani ko nta bwenge buhagije bufite kandi ko nta n'ubushishozi buhagije bufite" nyuma y'aho u Buyapani butangaje ko "umuntu wese uzava muri Koreya y'Epfo azamara ibyumweru bibiri mu kato gateganywa na leta".
Mu ntangiriro, ibikorwa by'abaturage bo muri Koreya y'Epfo byari bibujijwe cyane mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ingutu cy'umukuru w'igihugu Moon Jae-in.
Abanyakoreya benshi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko y'ubujurire y'ubutegetsi isaba ko ukwezi kw'ikirere guhanwa kubera ko iki cyorezo kirimo kwiyongera, cyangwa bashimira uko bitabiriye. Iki cyorezo cyatumye ibihugu bitangaza ibihe bidasanzwe mu guhangana nacyo.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo batanga impungenge ko bishobora gufasha leta gushimangira ububasha bwayo.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yemereye Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orbán kuyobora nta gihe ntarengwa, guhagarika inteko ishinga amategeko rimwe na rimwe, ndetse no guhagarika amatora no gufata ingamba ku bantu bakwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma kuri virusi n'ibyo leta irimo gukora mu guhangana n'ikibazo.
Icyorezo cya coronavirus cyatewe n'ibura ry'ibikoresho byinshi, kwiyongera kw'ikoreshwa ku isi mu kurwanya icyorezo, kugura ibintu bitunguranye, no guhagarika ibikorwa by'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze umuburo ko hari ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bishobora kubaho kubera ko abakoresha biyongera kandi abaguzi bakabura uko batanga ibikoresho.
Abantu benshi bo muri ako gace babonye ko hari ikibazo cy'ibikoresho by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, impapuro z'isuku n'amazi yabigenewe, byabuze kubera ko bari mu kaga.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cyatangaje ko hashobora kubaho gutinda mu gutwara ibikoresho by'amashanyarazi.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko ibisabwa ku bikoresho by'ubwirinzi byiyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongera inshuro makumyabiri ugereranyije n'ibiciro bisanzwe kandi ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byateba amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko ku isi hose hari ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, bituma abakozi bo mu rwego rw'ubuzima bahura n'akaga.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cy'isi cyatumye abaguzi ba Daegu babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Nubwo umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 ari mwinshi mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu karere ka Wuhan, uturere twombi twakize inzara bitewe n'ibura ry'ibiribwa.
