Gucunga ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 ni uburyo bwo kwirinda no gukumira icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Kugenzura neza ibyago mu kazi biterwa n'aho umuntu akorera n'ubwoko bw'akazi, gusuzuma aho ibyago bituruka, ikwirakwira ry'indwara mu baturage n'ibyago byo kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi (OSHA), imirimo y'ubwihebe buciriritse ni iyo ituma abantu n'abakozi bafatanya imirimo badahura cyane, bityo bikaba bisaba gufata ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, nko gukaraba intoki, gutuma abakozi baguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, guhumeka no gukomeza ibikorwa bisanzwe byo gusukura no kwirinda indwara.
Imirimo y'ibyago byo guhura n'ibiza ni abantu bakorana n'abantu batazwi cyangwa bakekwaho kuba bafite COVID-19, ariko bashobora kwandura bitewe n'ubwandu bukomeje cyangwa ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibi bikubiyemo abantu bava mu baturage, nko mu mashuri, ahantu hari abaturage benshi, no mu maduka manini.
Iki cyiciro kigomba kuba gifite ibikoresho byo guhumeka bikoresha imyuka ibanza guhumura neza, hamwe n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite mu gihe umuntu ufite COVID-19 ahura n'ikibazo cyo guhangana n'ibiza, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ubwandu bw'ibanze.
OSHA ifata abantu bafite ibyago bikomeye byo kwandura COVID-19 nk'abari mu kaga gakomeye, mu gihe abakozi bakora ibikorwa byo guhumeka mu kirere bakorakoranya ibipimo ku bantu bazwi cyangwa bakekwaho COVID-19.
Gutegeka impanuka neza kuri aba bakozi birimo kugenzura ubwubatsi, nko guhumeka ibihaha by'umuvuduko utagira umumaro n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite bikwiye akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kureka akazi kubera uburwayi, kwita ku bandi no gutinya guhura n'ibibazo.
