b'Angiotensin - converting enzyme 2 (ACE2) ni enzyme iba mu bice byo hanze by'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha, mu mitsi y'amaraso, mu mutima, mu mpyiko no mu mara.
ACE2 ikumira ibikorwa bya angotensin-converting enzyme (ACE) ifitanye isano, igabanya ingano ya angostatin-II kandi igatuma Ang (1-7) yiyongera, bigatuma iba intego yizewe yo kuvura indwara z'imitsi y'amaraso. ACE2 ikora nk'aho virusi zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi zinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Enzyme mu bantu ikunze kwitwa hACE2.
Angostantine-enzyme 2 ni zinc irimo icyuma, iboneka ku gice cy'imbere mu mubiri n'ibindi bice by'umubiri.
Poroteyine ya ACE2 ishyirwaho urubuga rwa N-terminal peptidase M2 na C-terminal collectrin renal amino acid transporter domain.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bwa I bw'urusobe rw'ibicurane, kuko iyi enzyme ifite uruziga rukora, kandi iba ku mapafu no ku bindi bice by'umubiri.
Icyiciro cya ACE2 cy'inyuma gicibwa n'indi enzyme yitwa Shadas mu gice cy'imbere cy'ingirabuzimafatizo, maze ikurikirwaho igashyirwa mu maraso nk'imyakura ikora mu maraso, amaherezo igashyirwa mu cyuma cy'umwotsi.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye cyane cyane na enzymes z'ingirabuzimafatizo z'umusemburo wa alveolar type II, mu nda nto, mu mitsi n'amaraso no mu bice byinshi by'umubiri.
Igikorwa cya ACE2 mRNA kiboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko, mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa neurone.
Uruhare rw'ingenzi rwa ACE2 ni ugukomeza uburinganire bwa ACE.
ACE ihindura ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin I ihinduka angiotensin II itera ku mwuka w'amaraso.
ACE2 nayo igabanya amino acide ya phenylalanine mu gice cy'umushongi wa carboxyl, ikayivamo angiotensin II (Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe) maze ikayihindura hydrolyzing mu bwoko bwa angiotestin (1-7), (H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH).
ACE2 ishobora guhosha ibindi bintu byinshi birimo [des-Arg9]-bradykinin, apelin, neurotensin, dynorphin A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi igenzura uruhu rwa SLC6A19, itwara amino acide idafite aho ihuriye, kandi izwiho kugira uruhare mu ndwara ya Heartburn.
Kimwe na poroteyine yo mu ruhu, ACE2 ikora nk'ahantu hanini ha kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo za koronavirusi zimwe na zimwe, harimo HCoV-NL63; SARS-CoV (virusi ituma SARS ibaho); na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituma COVID-19 ibaho).
By'umwihariko, poroteyine S1 z'udutsi tw'ingirabuzimafatizo za SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 zifatanya n'ingirabuzimafatizo zigize uruziga rwa ACE2 bigatuma virusi na za poroteyine biboneka mu ngirabuzimafatizo no mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ubu buryo bwo kwinjira mu mubiri busabwa kugenzura mbere ya poroteyine ya S kuri TMPRSS2 ikora poroteyine y'umwakiranyi, ubu ikaba ishobora kuba umuti ushyigikiwe n'ubushakashatsi. Ibi byatumye bamwe batekereza ko ishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu igabanya urugero rwa ACE2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ariko, imiryango myinshi y'inzobere n'inzego zishinzwe kugenzura zisaba gukomeza imiti isanzwe ya ACE inhibitor na ARB.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuvuzi n'ubumenyingiro (WHO) ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012, bwagaragaje ko gukoresha ACE inhibitors byagabanyije ubukana bw'ibicurane ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abatarayifite.
Byongeye kandi, ibyago byo kurwara pneumonia byari bimwe mu barwayi bavurwa ibicurane bya ACE bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara pneumonia, cyane cyane mu bwonko no mu mutima.
Gukoresha ACE inhibitors byarakoreshejwe mu gupima urupfu rufitanye isano na pneumonia, kandi ingaruka zari hasi cyane ugereranyije n'ibyago byo kurwara pneumonia muri rusange.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ya ACE2 (rhACE2) y'umuntu ivugwaho kuba uburyo bushya bwo kuvura indwara y'ibihaha ikomeye, ikongera imbaraga z'amaraso n'umwuka wa ogisijeni mu bana b'ingurube.
Ubuzima bwa kabiri bwa rhACE2 mu bantu ni amasaha agera kuri 10 kandi gutangira gukora kwayo ni iminota 30 uretse amasaha 24 y'akazi (igihe cy'amasaha).
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bugaragaza ko rhACE2 ishobora kuba umuti wizewe ku barwayi bafite cyangwa bafite ingufu nyinshi za angiotensin II z'ubuhinga bwa classic renin-angiotensin system inhibitors (RAS inhibitors). RhACE2 yasutswe mu bizamini byo kuvura indwara y'ubuhumekero ikomeye.
Porogaramu za COVID-19 ni porogaramu za mudasobwa zigenewe gufasha gukurikirana cyangwa gushaka abantu (abavugana) bashobora kuba barahuye n'umuntu wanduye.
Mu nzego zimwe na zimwe za leta n'intara, hari ibyangombwa byinshi byateguwe cyangwa byatanzwe hifashishijwe inkunga ya leta.
Imyubakire myinshi yashyizweho yo kubaka porogaramu zo gukurikirana abakoraho.
Ibibazo by'ibanga byatewe cyane cyane na sisitemu zishingiye ku gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Amahitamo yo kugabanya ubuhuha akubiyemo gukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugirango umenye aho umukozi ari hafi ya terefone zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bagiye gufatanya mu guhuza imikorere y'ibikoresho bikoresha Bluetooth na sisitemu z'imikorere ya Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yatangije porogaramu ya telefone ituma abaturage bamenya niba barigeze bahura n'abantu bafite COVID-19.
Ikoranabuhanga rya TraceTogether ryakoreshejwe mu mijyi isaga 200 yo mu Bushinwa.
Porogaramu yakozwe n'umuryango w'ikoranabuhanga wo muri ako gace, yasohotse nk'isoko ryuguruye, kandi itangazwa na leta. Intara ya Macédoine y'Amajyaruguru yatangije porogaramu ishingiye kuri Bluetooth, StopKorona!, kugirango ikurikirane ibyago by'abantu banduye kandi isubize vuba.
Porogaramu yakozwe na Minisiteri y'Itumanaho n'Ikoranabuhanga na Minisiteri y'Ubuzima.
Guhera ku ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu itegereje uruhushya rwo kuba kuri Google Play Store na Apple App Store.
"Ku ya 12 Mata, leta yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gushakisha abakundana iri mu cyiciro cyo kuzamura. Porogaramu nk'iyo iteganijwe muri Irilande no mu Bufaransa ("StopCovid") kandi izatangira gukora mu byumweru bike".
Australia na Nouvelle-Zélande byombi birimo gusuzuma porogaramu zishingiye kuri porogaramu ya TraceTogether na BlueTrace protocol yo muri Singapuru. Uburusiya buteganya gushyiraho porogaramu ya Geofencing ku barwayi ba COVID-19 baba i Moscou kugira ngo batava mu ngo zabo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'ubwubatsi bw'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yagaragaje ibibazo byinshi birimo ibisubizo by'ibinyoma bishobora gukoreshwa muri sisitemu zishingiye ku porogaramu hamwe n'uko gukoresha porogaramu bigomba guhagararira igice gito cy'abaturage.
"Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'impungenge z'ikwirakwira ry'ibikorwa byangiza cyangwa byangiza bya ""coronavirus"", Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku byiciro by'ibigo byashoboraga kongeramo porogaramu zijyanye na coronavirus mu bubiko bwa porogaramu, bigatuma ibazwa gusa ku bigo bya Facebook cyangwa ibigo bikomeye".
Google na Amazon bashyizeho amategeko amwe.
Abashinzwe umutekano bavuga ko bahangayikishijwe n'ingaruka z'ibikorwa byinshi byo kugenzura hakoreshejwe porogaramu za coronavirus, cyane cyane ko ibikorwa by'iperereza byashyizweho mu guhangana n'icyorezo cy'indwara ya coronavirus bishobora gusenyuka igihe cyose ibyago bizaba bimaze gushira.
Amnesty International n'andi mashyirahamwe arenga 100 yasabye ko ubwo buryo bwo kugenzura buhagarikwa.
Ibigo byatangaje ibintu umunani by'ibanze ku mishinga ya leta:
Gukurikirana bigomba kuba byemewe n'amategeko, ari ngombwa kandi bifite agaciro;
Uburebure bw'igenzura n'ubugenzuzi bugomba kuba bufite igipimo cy'umunsi;
Gukoresha amakuru bigomba kuba bigamije gusa COVID-19;
umutekano w'amakuru no guhisha amazina bigomba kurindwa kandi bigashyirwa ahagaragara hakurikijwe ibimenyetso;
Genzura ikoranabuhanga bigomba kwirinda kurengera no kutagira aho babogamira;
Gutanga amakuru yose ku bantu batatu bigomba kuba byemewe n'amategeko;
hakwiye kubaho uburyo bwo kurinda ibikorwa by'urugomo no kurinda uburenganzira bw'abaturage;
"Gushyira hamwe kw'ingenzi" kw'abagize uruhare bose, harimo inzego z'ubuzima rusange n'itsinda ryashinzwe, birakenewe. Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cya Keio cyo mu Budage (CCC) n'abanyamakuru (RSF) batanze urutonde rw'abantu bagomba kugenzurwa nta nkomyi".
Gahunda ya Google/Apple yo gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana ku mbuga zabo, niba bidakenewe, ni uburyo bwo gukemura ikibazo cyo gukurikirana.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byashyizeho uburyo bwo gukurikirana aho umuntu ari hakoreshejwe interineti aho gukoresha porogaramu, bikuraho ubushobozi bwo gukuramo porogaramu no kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Isirayeli, gukurikirana hakoreshejwe interineti byemewe.
Ibisubizo bishingiye kurubuga byo kugera kubitekerezo muburyo bwumutse bifite ibibazo bishobora kuvuka.
Ariko, sisitemu zose zifite seriveri nkuru ntabwo zigomba kubona amakuru yihariye yerekeye ahantu; uburyo bwinshi bwo kurinda ubuzima bwite bwashyizweho bukoresha seriveri nkuru gusa kumakuru (reba igice hepfo).
