Usibye gukoresha aya makuru, leta yashyizeho uburyo bwo kugeza amakuru y'ahantu kuri buri wese, bitewe n'ihinduka rikomeye ry'amategeko yerekeye ubuzima bwite bw'amakuru muri icyo gihugu kubera icyorezo cya MERS.
Aya makuru ashobora kuboneka ku bantu bose binyuze muri porogaramu nyinshi na website. Ibihugu birimo n'u Budage byatekereje gukoresha uburyo bwo kurinda abantu hagati n'imbere.
Kugeza kuri 6 Mata 2020, ntabwo amakuru aratangazwa.
Igitekerezo cyo kubahiriza ubuzima bwite no gukurikirana imikoranire cyariho mbere y'amateka manini y'ubushakashatsi bw'abantu, kandi cyatangiye nibura mu 2013. Ku ya 7 Mata 2020, ubwo bakoreshaga igisubizo cyubahiriza ubuzima bwite, ni ukuvuga igisubizo gikoresha Bluetooth Low Power (BLE), cyerekana uko hafi yari iri kuri terefone zindi.
Ariko, PPP-PT ni ubufatanye bukora mu buryo bw'ibanze kandi butari bwemewe kandi burimo protocole imwe, hamwe na protocole zihuriweho n'intara: gushakisha kure cyane ku bwirinzi bw'ibanga (DP-PPT / DP-3T), imibare y'igihe gito yo guhura, (TCN, FKA imibare y'ibyabaye, CEN), amategeko agenga ubuzima bwite no gushakisha itumanaho rya terefone igendanwa (PACT) n'ibindi.
Amakuru bwite agaragara muri izi porogaramu ntava mu gikoresho, kandi amakuru yose ajyanye nayo arashyirwa mubikoresho.
Itsinda ry'ibanga muri MIT Media Lab ririmo gukora SafePaths, urubuga rukoresha uburyo bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite mu gihe rukusanya no gukoresha amakuru yerekeye aho uri cyangwa aho unyura mu muhanda kugira ngo ukurikirane ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
""Amakuru ashingiye ku nyandiko yitwa ""Apps Gone Rogue: Kurinda ubuzima bwite bw'abantu mu gihe cy'icyorezo yasohotse ku ya 7 Werurwe 2020. Ikindi gikorwa nk'icyo cyashinzwe muri MIT Media Lab ni urubuga rwa SafeTrace rwakozwe na Enema MPC, ikigo gikora ikoranabuhanga ry'ibanga".
SafeTrace ni ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bitekanye, rituma abakoresha bashobora gusangira aho bari n'amakuru y'ubuzima n'abandi bakoresha n'abayobozi, batitaye ku bwisanzure bw'amakuru yabo.
Ku ya 5 Mata 2020, TCN ya Global Coordination yashyizweho mu buryo bw'ibanze mu buryo bumwe kandi ahanini mu matsinda ahuriweho n'amategeko ngenderwaho, hashyizweho itsinda ryo kugabanya icyuho no gukurikirana no gukangurira abantu bose.
