Icyitegererezo cya mbere muri batanu mu barwayi batandatu cyerekanye umubare munini w'indwara, naho icya gatandatu cyerekanye umubare munini w'indwara ku munsi wa kabiri umurwayi yagenzuwe.
Indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero Coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2) ni virusi nshya y'ubuhumekero ya mbere yanduye, yatangiriye mu bantu batatu bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan basanganywe indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero ifitanye isano n'indwara y'ibihaha.
Imico yose ya virusi nshya ya SARS-CoV-2 iboneka mu bwoko bwa coronaviruses.
Hasi y'umubiri w'umuntu, virusi yica isabune yo mu rugo, igaca mu gice cy'umubiri cy'ubwirinzi. SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano ya bugufi na SARS-CoV ya mbere.
Ibirenge ni bimwe mu bice byugarijwe cyane na COVID-19, kuko virusi igera ku ngirabuzimafatizo z'abakiranyi binyuze muri enzymes ya agostine enzyme 2 (ACE2), ikunda kuboneka mu ngirabuzimafatizo za II za alveolar mu bihaha.
Virusi ikoresha uruziga rwihariye (glyoproteine) rwitwa "inducer" (peplomer) kugira ngo ihuze na ACE2 maze yinjire mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Indwara y'umutima itera indwara y'umutima mu buryo bwihutirwa, igaragara mu bantu 12 ku ijana bavurirwa mu bitaro byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa.
Ibimenyetso by'umutima biri hejuru kubera ibisubizo by'ubuhumekero bw'uburyo n'ibibazo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara mu gihe cy'iterambere ry'indwara, ariko kwangirika gukomeye kw'umubiri w'umubiri bifitanye isano n'abakira ACE2 mu mutima.
Ibinyemamatwara bya ACE2 byerekana cyane mu mutima kandi bigira uruhare mu mikorere y'umutima.
Mu barwayi bafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bafite ECI, basanze hari umubyibuho ukabije w'amaraso (31%) n'umuvuduko w'amaraso utuma amaraso asubira mu mubiri (25%) kandi bishobora kuba bifitanye isano na prostate nyuma y'indwara.
Nubwo SARS-COV-2 ifite ubukana ku ngirabuzimafatizo z'ubuhumekero zigaragaza ACE2 mu kugaragaza ubukana bw'ubuhumekero, abarwayi bafite COVID-19 ikomeye bagaragaza ibimenyetso by'umuvuduko w'amaraso ukabije.
By'umwihariko, hari ibimenyetso byerekana ko ingirabuzimafatizo za T zituma indwara zandura zituma umuntu atagira ubuzima (GM-CSF-secretory T-cells) zifitanye isano n'indwara ya monocytosis n'indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Indwara ziterwa na lymphocyte na zo zagiye zivugwa mu gihe cyo gupima abantu bapfuye.
