Kuva ku ya 4 Mata 2020, ibizamini bya virusi (bishobora kumenya ubwandu bukomeye kandi umuntu yarigeze kurwara) byatangiye gukorwa, ariko ntibyakoreshejwe cyane.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'Abashinwa bugaragaza ko 60 kugeza kuri 70% by'ibipimo by'uburwayi ari byo byonyine byemeza ko umuntu ashobora kwivuza.
FDA yo muri Amerika yemeje iki cyemezo cyo kugenzura ku wa 21 Werurwe 2020. Amabwiriza y'igerageza yashyizwe ahagaragara n'ibitaro bya Zhongnan muri Kaminuza ya Wuhan, agaragaza uburyo bwo gutahura ubwandu bushingiye ku bimenyetso by'ubuvuzi n'ibyago by'ibicurane.
Ibice bibiri by'ibirahure byinshi by'ibirahuri biri hasi hamwe n'inyuma, inkomoko n'ibisate by'inyuma birasanzwe mu banduye mbere.
