Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'ubushakashatsi mu byerekeranye n'ubuvuzi bw'ibice by'umubiri:
Indwara y'ubuhumekero (macrococcygeal-pleurisy), indwara y'umutima (péricardite), indwara y'ibihaha (pulmonary embolism), n'imyanda yo mu bihaha (pneumonia)
Hari ubwoko bune bw'agakoko gatera ibicurane:
Indwara y'ibihaha yoroheje: ibihaha, indwara y'ibihaha, indwara ziterwa n'imbeba, kanseri y'ibihaha n'ibihaha binini cyane
Indwara ikomeye y'ibihaha: Ibyago byo kwangirika kwa alveolar (DAD) biherekejwe no kwandura kwa alveolar oxidative.
DAD ni imwe mu mpamvu z'indwara ikomeye yo guhumeka (ARDS) n'indwara y'umuvuduko w'amaraso uri hasi cyane.
