Abahanga mu by'ubuzima bita ku bantu barwaye COVID-19, CDC irasaba ko umuntu akoresha uburyo busanzwe bwo kwirinda, kwirinda no kwirinda umwuka, kandi ko umuntu ashyirwa mu cyumba cyo guhunga indwara z'umwuka (IIR). CDC ivuga amabwiriza yo gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda igihe icyorezo kizaba cyadutse.
