Nk'uko imibare ya Kaminuza ya Johns Hopkins ibigaragaza, umubare w'abantu bapfuye ku isi yose kuva ku ya 17 Mata 2020 ni 6.9% (153,822/ 2,240,191).
Imibare itandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'urupfu rw'ubwandu (CFR), kigaragaza umubare w'abantu bapfuye kubera ubwandu, hamwe n'umubare w'abantu bapfa kubera ubwandu (IFR), umubare w'abantu banduye (bavuwe n'abataravuwe) bapfa kubera ubwandu.
Kandi ibipimo ntabwo bigomba guhagarikwa igihe runaka kugeza igihe abantu bamwe na bamwe bazaba baretse gukingirwa.
