Abantu 69 (0.004% by'abaturage) bamaze guhitanwa na COVID-19.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'imfu zacyo bitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani, imibare y'abapfuye yari myinshi.
Ibyago bikomeye ku bagabo ni mu myaka 50 y'amavuko, aho icyuho kiri hagati y'abagabo n'abagore kiri hafi 90.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa ku bagabo wari 2.8 ku ijana, mu gihe ku bagore wari 1.7 ku ijana.
Impamvu nyayo zitera iryo tandukaniro ry'ibitsina ntiziramenyekana, ariko ibisekuru n'imiterere bishobora kuba ari byo bituma habaho iryo tandukaniro.
Mu ndwara zandurira mu gitsina, kunywa itabi bishobora gutuma abagabo bapfa cyane kurusha abagore, urugero nko kugira umuvuduko w'amaraso uri hasi ugereranyije n'abagabo.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye ni abagabo, naho 72% by'abapfuye bazize COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Amerika ntiyakurikiranye amakuru yerekeye imibonano mpuzabitsina afitanye isano n'ubwandu bwa COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko indwara z'ibyorezo nk'icyorezo cya Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka zitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Umubare munini w'abakozi b'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, ni abagore kandi bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virusi.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ryavuze ko izina ry'ibanze ry'iki cyorezo ari COVID-19.
Umuyobozi Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, Theodoros Adhanom Ghebreyesus, yavuze ko Coronavirus, virusi yatumye abantu 19 barwara, igihe bamenyekanaga bwa mbere: 31 Ukuboza 2019.
Mu rwego rwo kwirinda ivangura, izina ryashyizweho hakurikijwe amabwiriza mpuzamahanga, kugira ngo ridakumira abantu bo mu gace runaka (urugero: Ubushinwa), ubwoko bw'inyamaswa cyangwa itsinda ry'abantu. Virusi itera COVID-19 yitwa SARS-CoV-2.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rikoresha amagambo "virusi ya COVID-19" na "virusi itera COVID-19" mu itangazamakuru.
"Iyo ndwara na virusi byitwa ""Coronavirus"" mu buryo busanzwe".
Iyi virusi n'indwara byitwaga Coronavirus na Wuhan Coronavirus, aho byabonetse bwa mbere mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa.
Muri Mutarama 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatanze amabwiriza yo mu mwaka wa 2015 ku bijyanye no gukoresha amazina y'impumyi n'indwara y'indwara y'ubuhumekero idakira ya 2020-nCov na 2019-nCoV nk'amazina y'agateganyo ya virusi n'indwara.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, izina COVID-19 na SARS-CoV-2 byatangiye kwitwa.
Bitewe n'ubushobozi buke mu buryo busanzwe bwo gutanga ibicuruzwa, bamwe mu bakora ibikoresho bya digitale barimo gucapa ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'udupfunyika tw'amazuru n'ibice by'umwuka.
