Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rw'iyo ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi ku isi ku nkingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 burimo gukorwa n'imiryango ya leta, amatsinda y'abanyeshuri n'abashakashatsi mu nganda.
Muri Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryashyizeho igerageza rya Solidarity kugira ngo risuzume ingaruka z'imiti ine ya virusi iriho, igaragaza ko igira ingaruka nziza.
