Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira bukomeje kugeragezwa.
Mbere na mbere, abashakashatsi bafite intego yo gukora urukingo rushobora kurwanya virusi.
Gukoresha iyi virusi, yaba ikiri nzima cyangwa yapfuye, mu kurwanya indwara zikomeye mu mubiri w'umuntu mu guhangana n'ubwandu bushya bwa COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri ni urukingo ruto, rugamije gukora urukingo rukurikirana ibice bimwe na bimwe by'agakoko gatera indwara.
Ku bijyanye na SARS-CoV-2, ubwo bushakashatsi bwibanze kuri poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi gufata receptor ya ACE2.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni urukingo rwa nucleic acid (uburyo bushya bwo gukora inkingo za DNA cyangwa RNA).
Muri ubwo buryo, inkingo z'igerageza zigomba kugeragezwa ku mutekano n'imikorere. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, igeragezwa rya mbere ry'urukingo ryatangijwe mu mujyi wa Seattle ku bitangiye gukora bane.
Uru rukingo rufite kode y'imiterere itagira icyo itwaye yakuwe muri virusi itera iyo ndwara. Nubwo rwashyizwe ahagaragara nk'uburyo bwo kuvura SARS-COV-2 bushingiye ku rukingo rw'abantu, biravuguruzanya.
Kuva muri Mata 2020, hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 biri gukorwa.
Ubu bushakashatsi burimo gusuzuma uburyo bwo kuvura malaria bwemewe mbere, harimo n'ubushakashatsi bune bwemewe, burimo burindwi bwa hydrochloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Ubushakashatsi bw'Abashinwa ku miti ikoreshwa mu kurwanya virusi, bwagaragaje ko hari ibipimo icyenda byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye mu mpera za Mata.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari igenzura ry'imikorere y'abakandida mu buvuzi bw'urukingo na imiti ya COVID-19. Imiti myinshi ya virusi ivurwa na COVID-19 irimo Reflovir, Chloroquine na Hydrochlorothrin, Lopevia / Rutanavir na Lopeanavir / Rudonavir ifatanyije na interferon beta.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso bifatika byerekana akamaro k'igabanuka ry'ibiciro.
Abarwayi bavurwa mu buryo bw'impuhwe bagaragaje ko hari icyuho mu buvuzi.
Ibizamini byo kwa muganga byo mu cyiciro cya III birakomeje muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ibitero bya chloroquine, byakoreshejwe mu kuvura malariya, byatangiye kwigishwa mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ariko kandi, hagiye hatangwa amabwiriza yo gusuzuma ubushakashatsi.
Abayobozi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya n'Ubushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha chlorokin.
Ariko, ikigo cya Wuhan cya Virology cyatangaje ko nubwo ingano y'igarama imwe ku munsi ari ingirakamaro, inshuro ebyiri z'iyo ingano ishobora guteza akaga kandi ishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, Urwego rw'abaganga rufata abantu bafite COVID-19 rwatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa hydroxychloroquine na chloroxycine. Itegeko ngenderwaho ry'Ubushinwa ku ncuro ya 7 ririmo gukoresha intervirone, ribavirine cyangwa umfenovirine kuri COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko ibipimo byinshi bya ribavirin ari ngombwa mu gukingira SARS-CoV-2 muri vitro.
Nyuma yo kugaragaza ibipimo by'umuvuduko muto wa SARS-CoV-2, byasabwe ko Nitazoxanide ikoreshwa nk'inyongera mu bushakashatsi bwa vivo. Ubushakashatsi bwerekanye ko gukoresha poroteyine nyinshi za Tissue Protease Serine 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kuri SARS-CoV-2 binyuze mu guhura na ACE2 receptor.
Imiti ya chloroquine na hydrochlorotrucurine hamwe na arthromycin cyangwa idafite, ifite inzitizi zikomeye zituma umuryango w'abaganga udashobora gukoresha iyi miti nta bushakashatsi bwinyongera. Oseltamivir ntishobora kwanduza SARS-CoV-2 mu cyumba kandi nta ruhare ruzwi mu kuvura COVID-19.
Mu byiciro bya nyuma bya COVID-19 bikomeye, imiyaga y'ibicurane ishobora kuba ingorabahizi.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira imiterere ya cytocin. Tocilizumab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa nyuma yo kurangiza ubushakashatsi buciriritse.
Nyuma yo kugira ingaruka nziza ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bukomeye, ubu mu Butaliyani hari igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya kabiri cy'uburwayi.
